<view class="search">
<l-search-bar placeholder="搜索" bg-color="#f6f6f6"shape="circle"/>
</view>
<view class="title">专属场景歌单</view>
<image class="posts-image1" src="../../images/gd2.jpg"></image>
<image class="posts-image1" src="../../images/gd1.jpg"></image>
<image class="posts-image1" src="../../images/gd3.jpg"></image>
<text class="content1">电音与爱情的灵魂碰撞</text>
<text class="content2">音乐中享受黄昏\n时分的橘色城市</text>
